member.name: WS_HOST_NAMES
member.summary: A structure containing a list of host names.

member.name: WS_HOST_NAMES.hostNames
member.summary: A list of host names. Each host name can be a DNS name or an IPv4 or IPv6 address. IPv6 addresses are enclosed in brackets ('[' address ']').

member.name: WS_HOST_NAMES.hostNameCount
member.summary: The number of elements in the hostNames array.
